TITLE: Destructuring HTTP Context in Route Handler
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to destructure properties from the HTTP context in a route handler to access request data (URL, headers, query parameters, body) and send responses.
SOURCE: https://github.com/adonisjs/v6-docs/blob/main/content/docs/concepts/http_context.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
