TITLE: Nginx Configuration for AdonisJS Reverse Proxy
DESCRIPTION: Example Nginx configuration file for setting up a reverse proxy for an AdonisJS application. It handles HTTP traffic and forwards requests to the Node.js server.
SOURCE: https://github.com/adonisjs/v6-docs/blob/main/content/docs/getting_started/deployment.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: nginx
