TITLE: Defining Custom Redis Lua Commands with AdonisJS - TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates how to register a custom Lua script as a Redis command using the AdonisJS Redis service. The 'defineCommand' method sets up a 'release' command, specifying the number of keys and the Lua script to be executed on the Redis server. Dependencies include the '@adonisjs/redis/services/main' module, and the defined command will be available on all Redis connections within the application. Inputs are the command name, number of keys, and Lua script.
