SOURCE: https://github.com/adonisjs/v6-docs/blob/main/content/docs/references/exceptions.md#2025-04-22_snippet_22

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { errors } from '@adonisjs/core'
if (error instanceof errors.E_MISSING_ARG_VALUE) {
  console.log(error.commandName)
}
```

