TITLE: Adding Custom Webpack Plugins
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to extend webpack configuration with custom plugins using Encore's addPlugin method. The example adds the npm-install-webpack-plugin, which automatically installs missing dependencies.
SOURCE: https://github.com/adonisjs/v6-docs/blob/main/content/docs/old/http/assets_bundling_encore.md#2025-04-22_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
