TITLE: Creating Server Instance for AdonisJS Middleware Testing in Packages
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how to create a server instance for testing AdonisJS middleware in packages without booting an entire application, using the ServerFactory.
SOURCE: https://github.com/adonisjs/v6-docs/blob/main/content/docs/basics/middleware.md#2025-04-22_snippet_17

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { ServerFactory } from '@adonisjs/core/factories/http'

const server = new ServerFactory().create()
const pipeline = server.pipeline([
  UserLocationMiddleware
])
```

